IAN GILLAN Live In Anaheim - 2008 UK 2-CD set comprising 20 tracks recorded live at the famous House Of Blues Club in Anaheim, California at the end of 2006, and sees him present the best of his career as a solo artist [with material from most ofh is albums], rarities [like &#039;Have Love Will Travel&#039; he recorded on hard to find solo album by guitarist Michael Lee Jackson] and lots of Deep Purple Songs including the mega classics &#039;Smoke on The Water&#039; & &#039;Into The Fire&#039; alongside tracks that Purple rarely played, presented in sealed & stickered fold-out digipak sleeve
